=== 欧盟 ===
{{see also|{{tsl|en|Bernstein of Leigh v Skyviews & General Ltd}}}}
[[欧洲联盟|欧盟]]的版权指令（{{tsl|en|Directive 2001/29/EC|第2001/29/EC号指令}}）允许成员国在其版权法内包含全景自由条款，但不作强制要求。<ref name="eu">N.N.: ''[http://www.fotocommunity.de/info/Panoramafreiheit#Europa_hilft Panoramafreiheit] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fotocommunity.de/info/Panoramafreiheit#Europa_hilft |date=20150418173225 }}''. {{de}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://ipkitten.blogspot.co.uk/2015/06/freedom-of-panorama-what-is-going-on-at.html|title=The IPKat|work=ipkitten.blogspot.co.uk|language=en|access-date=2016-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626204251/http://ipkitten.blogspot.co.uk/2015/06/freedom-of-panorama-what-is-going-on-at.html|archive-date=2015-06-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[德国|德国]]版权法（{{Lang|de|Urheberrechtsgesetz}}）在第59条定义了全景自由概念，<ref name="de">{{cite web|last1=Seiler|first1=David|title=Fotografieren von und in Gebäuden|url=http://www.fotorecht.de/publikationen/gebaeude.html|publisher=visuell|accessdate=2007-09-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160521183732/http://www.fotorecht.de/publikationen/gebaeude.html|archivedate=2016-05-21|page=50|language=de|date=2001|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[英国|英国]]的《{{tsl|en|Copyright, Designs and Patents Act 1988|1988年版权，工业品外观设计和专利法}}》第62条中也有类似表述。<ref name="uk">{{cite web|last1=Lydiate|first1=Henry|title=Advertising and marketing art: Copyright confusion|url=http://www.artquest.org.uk/articles/view/advertising-and-marketing-art-copyright-confusion1|website=Artquest|accessdate=2007-09-20|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422063515/http://www.artquest.org.uk/articles/view/advertising-and-marketing-art-copyright-confusion1|archivedate=2016-04-22|language=en|date=1991|dead-url=no}}</ref>这类规定在其他几个国家<ref name="koetz">Koetz, D.: ''[https://web.archive.org/web/20060527190204/http://www.photographie.de/magazin/fotorecht_10_2002.cfm Erlaubnis zum Ablichten von Sehenswürdigkeiten]'', in ''Photographie'' 10/2002. {{de}}</ref>（或者说“多数成员国”<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blogs.ec.europa.eu/ECintheUK/europe-is-not-banning-tourist-photos-of-the-london-eye/|title=Euromyths and Letters to the Editor: Europe is not banning tourist photos of the London Eye|publisher=European Commission in the UK|language=en|access-date=2016-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150626140222/http://blogs.ec.europa.eu/ECintheUK/europe-is-not-banning-tourist-photos-of-the-london-eye/|archive-date=2015-06-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>）中都有存在。

欧盟内也存在完全没有全景自由的国家，例如[[意大利|意大利]]<ref name="it">Spinelli, L. ''[http://punto-informatico.it/2030219/PI/News/wikipedia-cede-al-diritto-autore-italiota.aspx Wikipedia cede al diritto d'autore] {{Wayback|url=http://punto-informatico.it/2030219/PI/News/wikipedia-cede-al-diritto-autore-italiota.aspx |date=20080929014738 }}'', Punto Informatico. {{it}}</ref>和[[冰岛|冰岛]]<ref name="is">Salvör Gissurardóttir ''[http://salvor.blog.is/blog/salvor/entry/977597/ Bannað að birta mynd af Hallgrímskirkju] {{Wayback|url=http://salvor.blog.is/blog/salvor/entry/977597/ |date=20160818073402 }}'', blog entry. {{is}}</ref>。尽管意大利发生过多次抗议<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.grillini.it/show.php?4884|title=Diritto di panorama|accessdate=2008-08-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081025001151/http://www.grillini.it/show.php?4884|archivedate=2008-10-25|language=it|dead-url=no}}</ref>和一次由律师{{lang|it|Guido Scorza}}及强调这一问题的记者{{tsl|en|Luca Spinelli}}发起的<ref name="it" />全国提案，<ref>Scorza, G., Spinelli, L., ''[http://www.diritto.it/all.php?file=25583.pdf Dare un senso al degrado] {{Wayback|url=http://www.diritto.it/all.php?file=25583.pdf |date=20090708045222 }}''. {{it}}</ref>但依照旧有的意大利版权法，发布公共场所的摄影复制品仍然受到禁止。<ref>''[http://www.normattiva.it/uri-res/N2Ls?urn:nir:stato:legge:1941-04-22;633!vig= Legge 22 aprile 1941 n. 633] {{Wayback|url=http://www.normattiva.it/uri-res/N2Ls?urn:nir:stato:legge:1941-04-22;633!vig= |date=20141223012833 }}''. {{it}}</ref><ref>''[http://www.camera.it/parlam/leggi/deleghe/testi/04042dl.htm Decreto Legislativo 22 gennaio 2004, n. 42] {{Wayback|url=http://www.camera.it/parlam/leggi/deleghe/testi/04042dl.htm |date=20081024122502 }}''. {{it}}</ref>这一限制在一部名为{{tsl|it|Codice dei beni culturali e del paesaggio|意大利文化风景和遗产法|文化风景和遗产法}}的法律中得到加强，该法规定以商业目的发布“文化物品”（理论上包括所有具有文化和艺术价值的对象和地点）的图片前必须获得艺术和文化遗产部在当地分支机构（即{{Lang|it|Soprintendenza}}）的授权。

包括[[法国|法国]]在内的一些国家则不对包含公共空间内艺术创作品（如建筑或雕塑）的图像全部许可，这些国家仅在“偶然包含”的情况下允许这类包含版权作品的图像。在法国，如果图像中包含的版权作品不是作为次要部分或图像背景，而是有意包含或作为其中心及基本主题使用，则图像需要取得此作品作者（而不是所有者）的授权。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://legifrance.gouv.fr/affichCodeArticle.do?idArticle=LEGIARTI000006278875&cidTexte=LEGITEXT000006069414&dateTexte=20120705&oldAction=rechCodeArticle|title=Article L.112-2 du Code de la propriété intellectuelle|accessdate=2012-07-20|date=1992-07-01|publisher=Legifrance.gouv.fr|language=fr|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150701005350/http://legifrance.gouv.fr/affichCodeArticle.do?idArticle=LEGIARTI000006278875&cidTexte=LEGITEXT000006069414&dateTexte=20120705&oldAction=rechCodeArticle|archive-date=2015-07-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==== 诉讼 ====
欧盟内各国立法的不同引发了一些诉讼，其中一个例子是{{tsl|de|Hundertwasserentscheidung|汉德瓦萨裁决}}。[[佛登斯列·汉德瓦萨|佛登斯列·汉德瓦萨]]在这次案件中胜诉，事件的起因是一家德国公司使用了一张包含奥地利建筑物的照片。<ref>{{cite web |title=BGH, 05.06.2003 - I ZR 192/00 |url=https://dejure.org/dienste/vernetzung/rechtsprechung?Text=I%20ZR%20192/00 |website=dejure.org |accessdate=2016-10-28 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820052628/https://dejure.org/dienste/vernetzung/rechtsprechung?Text=I%20ZR%20192%2F00 |archivedate=2016-08-20 |language=de |date=2003-06-05 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

另一起诉讼与版权无关，但是牵涉到{{tsl|it|Codice dei beni culturali e del paesaggio|意大利文化风景和遗产法}}。这场意大利文化遗产与活动部和Stoneage公司之间的诉讼（{{lang|it|Ministero dei Beni e delle Attività Culturali vs. Stoneage S.r.l. (Cass. civ. Sez. VI - 1 Ordinanza, 23-04-2013, n. 9757, rv. 626365)}}）一直上诉到了[[義大利最高法院|意大利最高法院]]。

2016年4月4日，{{tsl|en|Supreme Court of Sweden|瑞典最高法院}}裁定[[维基媒体分会列表|瑞典维基媒体协会]]制作瑞典公共艺术品数据库和网站的行为侵犯了艺术家的版权，该等数据库和网站中包含由公众自行上传的公共艺术品。<ref name="falkvinge-2016">{{Cite web|url=https://www.privateinternetaccess.com/blog/2016/04/supreme-court-wikipedia-violates-copyright-posting-photos-public-art/|title=Supreme Court: Wikimedia violates copyright by posting its own photos of public, taxpayer-funded art|accessdate=2016-09-08|date=2016-04-04|last=Falkvinge|first=Rick|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-35969734|title=Wikimedia Sweden art map 'violated copyright'|date=5 April 2016|work=BBC News|accessdate=2016-09-09|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160923151732/http://www.bbc.com/news/technology-35969734|archive-date=2016-09-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://blog.wikimedia.org/2016/04/04/strike-against-freedom-panorama/|title=A strike against freedom of panorama: Swedish court rules against Wikimedia Sverige|accessdate=2016-09-09|date=2016-04-04|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160921153722/https://blog.wikimedia.org/2016/04/04/strike-against-freedom-panorama/|archive-date=2016-09-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>瑞典版权法中对版权所有者享有的将作品公开这一排他性权利有例外规定，这项规定允许其他人描摹公共艺术品，<ref name="Wikimedia Sweden decision">{{Cite court|litigants=Bildupphovsrätt i Sverige ek. för. v. Wikimedia Svierge|vol=|reporter=|opinion=|pinpoint=|court={{tsl|en|Supreme Court of Sweden|瑞典最高法院}}|date=2016-04-04|url=https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/foundation/e/ec/TheSwedishSupremeCourtsDecisionBUSvWikimediaFINAL-English_Translation.pdf|quote=|language=en}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>{{Rp|2-5}}但瑞典最高法院决定用更具限制性的眼光看待这项版权例外规定。<ref name="Wikimedia Sweden decision" />{{Rp|6}}法院认为，无论是对于数据库操作者还是访问者，这样的数据库都包含的商业价值都不算小，而“这种价值应当为艺术品作者所保留。这与操作者是否真的将数据库用于商业目的无关。”<ref name="Wikimedia Sweden decision" />{{Rp|6}}案件随后发回下级法院审理，下级法院负责确定瑞典维基媒体协会给发起这场诉讼的{{tsl|en|Collective rights management|版权集体管理}}组织“瑞典视觉艺术版权联盟”（{{lang|sv|Bildkonst Upphovsrätt i Sverige}}，简称BUS）造成的损失，此组织在这次诉讼中代表相关艺术家。<ref name="Wikimedia Sweden decision" />{{Rp|2,7}}

=== 澳大利亚 ===
[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]在联邦法律《{{tsl|en|Copyright law of Australia#Copyright Act 1968|1968年版权法}}》的第65至68节中处理全景自由问题。该法第65节规定，“……被非临时性地放置在公共场所或向公众开放之场所的作品，它的版权不因制作绘画、绘图、雕刻、摄影，或包含入影片或电视广播而受损害。”这项规定适用于任何“艺术作品”，即该法第10节(c)段定义的“具有艺术工艺的作品”（电路设计除外）。<ref name="AU">''[http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/legis/cth/consol_act/ca1968133/ Copyright Act 1968] {{Wayback|url=http://www.austlii.edu.au/au/legis/cth/consol_act/ca1968133/ |date=20161125143839 }}'' (Cth) {{en}}</ref>

然而，“[[街頭藝術|街头艺术]]”在该国可能受版权保护。<ref name="G124v01">{{Cite web|url=http://www.copyright.org.au/acc_prod/AsiCommon/Controls/BSA/Downloader.aspx?iDocumentStorageKey=62a2e433-4cab-4d6f-8dd2-dc4af24277e7&iFileTypeCode=PDF&iFileName=Street%20Art%20&%20Copyright|title=Street Art & Copyright|accessdate=2016-05-08|date=2014-09|work=Information Sheet G124v01|publisher={{tsl|en|Australian Copyright Council|澳大利亚版权委员会}}|language=en|format=PDF|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322193002/http://www.copyright.org.au/acc_prod/AsiCommon/Controls/BSA/Downloader.aspx?iDocumentStorageKey=62a2e433-4cab-4d6f-8dd2-dc4af24277e7&iFileTypeCode=PDF&iFileName=Street%20Art%20&%20Copyright|archive-date=2016-03-22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.artslaw.com.au/info-sheets/info-sheet/street-photographers-rights/|title=Street photographer's rights|accessdate=2016-05-08|publisher=Arts Law Centre of Australia|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630101936/http://www.artslaw.com.au/info-sheets/info-sheet/street-photographers-rights/|archivedate=2014-06-30|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.copyright.org.au/admin/cms-acc1/_images/732757805533a4bbed9e2a.pdf|title=Photographers & Copyright|accessdate=2014-10-28|date=2014-01|format=PDF|publisher=Australian Copyright Council|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702180313/http://www.copyright.org.au/admin/cms-acc1/_images/732757805533a4bbed9e2a.pdf|archivedate=2014-07-02|quote=You will generally need permission to photograph other public art, such as murals.|language=en|dead-url=no}}</ref>

